            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>截至台北時間16日12:20，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲649.79點（或2.11%），暫報31460.37點。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li>近 1 週：+1.48%</li><li>近 1 月：+10.56%</li><li>近 3 月：+12.96%</li><li>近 6 月：+34.92%</li><li>今年以來：+4.98%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>焦點個股</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>轉單利多概念領漲+7.34%。其中    世界(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:5347:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5347\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5347-TW</a>)            上漲        9.84%            ;        旺宏(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2337:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2337\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2337-TW</a>)            上漲        9.05%            ;        華邦電(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2344:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2344\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2344-TW</a>)            上漲        7.86%    。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>工具機概念領漲+5.44%。其中    健椿(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4561:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4561\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4561-TW</a>)            上漲        9.86%            ;        福裕(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4513:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4513\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4513-TW</a>)            上漲        9.84%            ;        喬福(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1540:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1540\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1540-TW</a>)            上漲        6.87%    。</p></section></main>",
